# CollisionMode

**Static Property**

A static property that allows you to access the annotation’s collision mode enumeration values.

## Declaration

```swift
static CollisionMode: typeof CollisionMode;
```

## Discussion

Use this object to access the [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/Annotation/CollisionMode-data.var] enumeration with `mapkit.Annotation.CollisionMode`.

## Static properties

- **DisplayPriority**: A static property that allows you to access the available display priority enumeration values.
